text: OMG!! Not a big fan of Nasi Lemak.  The moment i tasted this stall's rice. I'm sold! They use basmati rice, soft, fluffy and fragrance is just nice. Not to memtion the ikanbilis sambal is so delicious! Gulp down within 5 mins! Shiok & cheap! #01-96 Super shiok Nasi Lemak, lives up to its name!! Otah set $3.6.

This is my offday favourite lunch place. All the way from Bedok to here for these 2 foods. This boneless chicken rice honestly is the best. Fragrance rice, thick and juicy chicken, fresh ginger and chili paste, if you want can put black soysauce. Chicken rice closed every Monday. And prefer this ÊñáÂçécoffee stall, not only they provide gau coffee, the boss can remember all regular customers past orders, extreme good memories.

Worth the trip.

07/March/2025
Visited this market after had my breakfast at the Food Centre. Wet & dried goods were available.
I wanted to use the restroom before I leave market. But I was told that the toilet fee collection do not accepts 5cents coin. ü§î
